  <entry>
    <title>Linux Apache2多端口部署</title>
    <url>/2025/02/06/linux%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85apache2/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h3 id="Linux-Apache2多端口部署"><a href="#Linux-Apache2多端口部署" class="headerlink" title="Linux Apache2多端口部署"></a>Linux Apache2多端口部署</h3><h4 id="1，安装Apache2"><a href="#1，安装Apache2" class="headerlink" title="1，安装Apache2"></a>1，安装Apache2</h4><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">sudo</span> apt update</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">sudo</span> apt install apache2</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h4 id="2，找到ports-conf文件"><a href="#2，找到ports-conf文件" class="headerlink" title="2，找到ports.conf文件"></a>2，找到ports.conf文件</h4><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> /etc/apache2</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">ls</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">root@nine:~# <span class="built_in">cd</span> /etc/apache2/</span><br><span class="line">root@nine:/etc/apache2# <span class="built_in">ls</span></span><br><span class="line">apache2.conf    conf-enabled  magic           mods-enabled  sites-available</span><br><span class="line">conf-available  envvars       mods-available  ports.conf    sites-enabled</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h4 id="3，编辑ports-conf文件"><a href="#3，编辑ports-conf文件" class="headerlink" title="3，编辑ports.conf文件"></a>3，编辑ports.conf文件</h4><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">vim ports.conf</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h4 id="4，添加端口，如下"><a href="#4，添加端口，如下" class="headerlink" title="4，添加端口，如下"></a>4，添加端口，如下</h4><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># If you just change the port or add more ports here, you will likely also</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># have to change the VirtualHost statement in</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># /etc/apache2/sites-enabled/000-default.conf</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># sports-memory</span></span><br><span class="line">Listen 23106</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># blog</span></span><br><span class="line">Listen 23107</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># wprdpress</span></span><br><span class="line">Listen 23108</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&lt;IfModule ssl_module&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        Listen 443</span><br><span class="line">&lt;/IfModule&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&lt;IfModule mod_gnutls.c&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        Listen 443</span><br><span class="line">&lt;/IfModule&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># vim: syntax=apache ts=4 sw=4 sts=4 sr noet</span></span><br><span class="line">~                                                                                                           ~     </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>添加后，保存退出（<code>:wq</code>）</p>
<h4 id="5，添加站点（sites-available）"><a href="#5，添加站点（sites-available）" class="headerlink" title="5，添加站点（sites.available）"></a>5，添加站点（sites.available）</h4><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> sites-available/</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">root@nine:/etc/apache2# <span class="built_in">cd</span> sites-available/</span><br><span class="line">root@nine:/etc/apache2/sites-available# <span class="built_in">ls</span></span><br><span class="line">000-default.conf  default-ssl.conf</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>编辑站点</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">vim 000-default.conf</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;VirtualHost *:23106&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        ServerAdmin webmaster@localhost</span><br><span class="line">        DocumentRoot /var/www/html</span><br><span class="line">        ErrorLog <span class="variable">$&#123;APACHE_LOG_DIR&#125;</span>/error.log</span><br><span class="line">        CustomLog <span class="variable">$&#123;APACHE_LOG_DIR&#125;</span>/access.log combined</span><br><span class="line">&lt;/VirtualHost&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&lt;VirtualHost *:23107&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        ServerAdmin webmaster2@localhost</span><br><span class="line">        DocumentRoot /var/www/blog/dist</span><br><span class="line">        ErrorLog <span class="variable">$&#123;APACHE_LOG_DIR&#125;</span>/error.log</span><br><span class="line">        CustomLog <span class="variable">$&#123;APACHE_LOG_DIR&#125;</span>/access.log combined</span><br><span class="line">&lt;/VirtualHost&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&lt;VirtualHost *:23108&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        ServerAdmin webmaster3@localhost</span><br><span class="line">        DocumentRoot /var/www/wordpress</span><br><span class="line">        ErrorLog <span class="variable">$&#123;APACHE_LOG_DIR&#125;</span>/error.log</span><br><span class="line">        CustomLog <span class="variable">$&#123;APACHE_LOG_DIR&#125;</span>/access.log combined</span><br><span class="line">&lt;/VirtualHost&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>编辑完成后，保存退出（<code>:wq</code>）</p>
<h4 id="6，重启Apache2服务"><a href="#6，重启Apache2服务" class="headerlink" title="6，重启Apache2服务"></a>6，重启Apache2服务</h4><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">systemctl restart apache2</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h4 id="7-卸载apache2"><a href="#7-卸载apache2" class="headerlink" title="7. 卸载apache2"></a>7. 卸载apache2</h4><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">apt remove apache2</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<pre><code>
</code></pre>
]]></content>
